{"tid":1038170,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我啲假期 除咗用嚟返工 就無其他嘢做了⋯","createTime":"2019-02-26T12:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T13:17:42.000Z","uid":78683,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"51e418ccab0572ba1e61d052663040c0f63d2c66","tid":1038170,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T12:59:56.000Z","msg":"人哋年假係去旅行 <br />\n我年假用嚟返炒散<br />\n<br />\n人哋紅日連假係同朋友去玩<br />\n我紅日連假用嚟炒散<br />\n<br />\n人哋星期六日去休息放鬆<br />\n我星期六日用嚟返炒散<br />\n<br />\n今日返工畀同事問「依家先見到你原來個個星期六都要返工」<br />\n我笑咗一笑 <br />\n啱啱喺到諗 我好似呢幾年都係係咁返工 其實好攰<br />\n不過除咗返工 我就諗唔到自己可以做啲咩<br />\n得返工可以麻醉到自己 唔使諗其他嘢<br />\n一靜就會唔開心亂諗嘢 咁唔好靜咪得 <br />\n係咁返工返工返工返到好攰 攰就瞓教 瞓醒就返工 日復日 <br />\n又準備瞓了 聽日繼續返工"},{"pid":"0c3b0769e7d70f449dfbda45e730f1275ce682bf","tid":1038170,"uid":236602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T13:01:27.000Z","msg":"包個ptbf去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ff3b52f72cf95ba837da19a1714fcb67593a6c","tid":1038170,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T13:02:15.000Z","msg":"有錢咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c837fbeba6f659857b8372f532f6f2403ba6cd8","tid":1038170,"uid":2106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T13:02:24.000Z","msg":"叫下🐔"},{"pid":"0a46e93c9d4579bbef4a92d186cbb2f7630bbb25","tid":1038170,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T13:08:38.000Z","msg":"我反而想好似你咁勤力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一放假無野做 都唔想番工<br />\n但又無錢用"},{"pid":"0780d52480e79e8c95213b63b09466446da35d95","tid":1038170,"uid":116131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T13:17:42.000Z","msg":"瞓多啲覺，搵下興趣班學下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲one day workshop試下新野<br />\n<br />\n我真係無可能咁勤力 日日放假淨係想瞓覺"}]}